---

## â–¶ï¸ How to Run the Project

1. Create & activate virtual environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate   # Windows
```

2. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install flask flask-sqlalchemy
```

3. Run the Flask app

```bash
python wsgi.py
```

4. Open browser and visit:

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000/
```

